abstract: I write you from the birthplace of the Constitution of Kansas. Three times have the people essayed, legally and peacefully, to emancipate themselves from the Federal yoke; and wo be to that party which shall again attempt to defeat their righteous efforts. abstract: The case of a man named JANOWVITZ, recently decided in Montreal, has created some interest in that city. abstract: At 1 o'clock this afternoon, the bark Wyman, Capt. BARKER, sailed on an expedition to the Northern Atlantic Ocean to survey a route for a telegraphic cable by way of Greenland, Iceland and the Shetland Islands, to Glasgow. The vessel has been chartered by Col. T. P. SHAFFNER, who goes in her, accompanied by his wife and son, and two gentlemen of Worcester.

abstract: We have been besieged with inquiries as to the truth of the telegraphic report in this morning's paper concerning the rumored loss of the frigate Congress.
